The classloader mechanism had been changed in 3.2.3 released. In former days, the classloader of classes in plugin jars are different with the classes of the enhanced classes. That is a big change. So you can't use the same package name to access the a `package-level` class.

This need to fix fast, to make sure the plugins works perfectly.
